Room.Name: Netherworld Lane
Room.ShortDescription: You are traveling along Netherworld Lane, south of a large housing complex.
Room.LongDescription: Housing is usually not a problem in Oceancrest as long as you don't mind living in one of the two large housing complexes. There is no room for individual houses within the borders of Oceancrest, so many people build houses outside of the city. However, most feel more secure living inside the City Walls and have learned to survive, in relative comfort, in these housing complexes.
